                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d601">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">839.51/3906: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in the Dominican Republic</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schoenfeld</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-05-22T10:00:00-05:00"
                            >May 22, 1933—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 10:50 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>24. Your personal letter May 13. Mr. Davies yesterday informed me that he had
                    concluded an agreement with the Dominican Government to act as General Counsel
                    for them in financial and related matters. The President confirmed this
                    information. Mr. and Miss Davies leave by air tomorrow morning.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Schoenfeld</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
